                                    Congress passed 352 bills and resolutions in its last session — states passed 45,000+.
We reached out to reporters in every state and asked them to identify and analyze the top 5 issues their state is currently facing.
The result is a unique, comprehensive policy breakdown of the most pressing issues facing the nation right now.
                                
After reading this report, you will learn:

Hit the ground running: our intuitive interface cuts down the learning curve
See every bill that matters: our reports pull all the bills on your issues with just a few clicks
Be a resource: integrate StateTrack with your website and create a powerful action center
Track with confidence: we post new bills up to 24 hours faster than the competition








