ADVOCACY  Trademark Information
 Advocacy Wealth Management Services, LLC
Structured financial planning services; financial consultation, namely, designing financial solutions for settlements of legal claims that work in concert with structured annuities; financial consulting services for attorneys, litigants, and financial professionals in designing settlements of legal claims




Perfect for these industries

Insurance & Financial Services





Words that describe this mark
structured   financial   planning   services   financial   consultation         designing   financial   solutions   settlements   legal   claims   work   concert   structured   annuities   financial   consulting   services   attorneys      litigants      financial    
                                    




This is a brand page for the ADVOCACY trademark by Advocacy Wealth Management Services, LLC 
                                in Atlanta, GA, 30305.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this ADVOCACY trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Advocacy Wealth Management Services, LLC of the ADVOCACY trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the ADVOCACY trademark.
                           






On Friday, May 21, 2010,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        ADVOCACY by 
                        Advocacy Wealth Management Services, LLC, Atlanta, GA  30305.
                        The USPTO has given the ADVOCACY 
                        trademark serial  number of  85044763.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED.
                        The correspondent listed for ADVOCACY is 
                        
                        
                                            ELLEN S. SIMPSON of 
                                            SIMPSON & SIMPSON, PLLC,  5555 MAIN ST, WILLIAMSVILLE, NY 14221-5430 
                                .
                            The ADVOCACY trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for ADVOCACY 
                            is Structured financial planning services; financial consultation, namely, designing financial solutions for settlements of legal claims that work in concert with structured annuities; financial consulting services for attorneys, litigants, and financial professionals in designing settlements of legal claims. 
                            





